Package edu.usc.pgroup.goffish.gofs

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    INameNode
    This interface represents a central authority which contains mappings from partition ids to the locations of those partitions.
    IPartition
    A partition represents a subset of the vertices and edges in a graph.
    ISerializablePartition
    This interface represents a partition which is suitable for serialization by ISliceManager.
    ISliceManager
    This interface represents a object capable of writing and reading partitions and their associated instance data.
    ISubgraph
    This interface represents a weakly connected component within a partition, and the associated instance data.
    ISubgraphInstance
    This represents a single instance of data associated with a subgraph.
    ISubgraphObjectProperties
    This represents a set of property values for a single object, an edge or vertex.
    ISubgraphTemplate
    This interface represents a subgraph template, which contains the structure of the subgraph, i.e.
  • Class Summary

    Property
    This class represents a single property that an instance might contain values for.
    PropertySet
    This class represents a set of properties and supports collection oriented methods over those properties.
